        "chatId": "8266195913",
        "text": "=⚠️ *Production Pipeline XATOLIK*\n\n📅 Sana: {{ $('📋 Fetch Today\\'s Task').item.json.Date }}\n📝 Mavzu: {{ $('📋 Fetch Today\\'s Task').item.json.Topic_UZ }}\n❌ Xatolik: {{ $json.message || 'Noma\\'lum xatolik' }}\n\nn8n dashboardni tekshiring.",
        "additionalFields": { "parse_mode": "Markdown" }
      },
